'''Egil Selvik''' (born 30 July 1997) is a Norwegian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[EFL Championship]] club [[Watford F.C.|Watford]] and the [[Norway national football team|Norway national team]].<ref>{{Soccerway|egil-selvik/408410}}</ref>

==Club career==
On 25 November 2024, Selvik was sent off for receiving both red and yellow cards in a 5–1 league victory against [[FK Haugesund]].<ref>{{Cite web|first1=Elise|last1=Pedersen|first2=Øystein|last2=Ellingsen|first3=Johan|last3=Mihle Laugaland|title=Viking beklager: "Dette ble feil og dumt"|url=https://www.nrk.no/rogaland/fkhs-egil-selvik-fikk-rodt-kort-etter-at-han-_klappet_-viking-spiller-i-ansiktet-_-viking-beklager-1.17141675|publisher=[[NRK]]|date=25 November 2024|access-date=10 January 2025|language=no}}</ref> In his last match for [[FK Haugesund]] on 8 December, he kept a clean sheet to seal Haugesund to a 2–0 league victory against [[FK Moss]].<ref>{{Cite news|first=Stine|last=Grøtting|title=Landslagskeeper Egil Selvik bekrefter at han er ferdig i Haugesund|url=https://www.dagbladet.no/studio/sportstudio/307?post=174553|newspaper=[[Dagbladet]]|publisher=[[Aller Media]]|date=8 December 2024|access-date=10 January 2025|language=no}}</ref>

On 10 January 2025, Selvik moved abroad to Italy, signing a contract with [[Udinese Calcio|Udinese]].<ref>{{Cite press release|title=Egil Selvik è bianconero|url=https://www.udinese.it/news/squadra/egil-selvik-e-bianconero|website=Udinese|date=10 January 2025|language=it}}</ref> However, Selvik was only at Udinese for a matter of weeks before moving on to [[EFL Championship]] club [[Watford F.C.|Watford]] for an undisclosed fee on 31 January.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-01-31 |title=Egil Selvik: Watford sign Udinese goalkeeper for undisclosed fee |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/articles/c805xx7jrrlo |access-date=2025-01-31 |website=BBC Sport |language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-01-31 |title=Official: Selvik Signs |url=https://www.watfordfc.com/news/2025/january/31/official-selvik-signs/ |access-date=2025-12-12 |website=Watford FC}}</ref>

==International career==
Selvik debuted for the [[Norway national football team|Norwegian senior squad]] on 7 September 2023 in a friendly match against [[Jordan national football team|Jordan]].<ref>{{Cite web|first1=Henrik|last1=Hovi|first2=Eirik|last2=Nesset Hjelvik|title=Egil (27) skal redde Norge: "Haaland tjener sikkert ti ganger mer på en uke"|url=https://www.tv2.no/sport/egil-27-skal-redde-norge-haaland-tjener-sikkert-ti-ganger-mer-pa-en-uke/17157597/|publisher=[[TV 2 (Norwegian TV channel)|TV 2]]|date=12 November 2024|access-date=10 January 2025|language=no}}</ref>

